[normal] We do not consider foodbanks to be a good alternative as
[normal] donations are 
[normal]limited to non-perishable food. We would like to see a proper study of the effect on health for people who have a prolonged reliance on food banks.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]We are offering a number of support projects, such as help in getting back into employment, cooking on a budget, confidence courses, computer courses and budgeting courses, all offered on both a
[normal]n individual 
[normal]and group basis.
